arCallbacks.szOnCallbackCompleteScript:
function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)
	
	--Door Controls + Donan advancing
	Hydra.ActorDelete(ID_DOOR_SP)
	Hydra.ActorGizmoOperate(ID_DOOR)
	Hydra.QActorWait(ID_DONAN_ENTRANCE, 1.5)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(ID_DONAN_ENTRANCE, LOC_DONAN_BEYOND, "NPC_RUN", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(ID_DONAN_ENTRANCE, LOC_DONAN_BEYOND)
	Hydra.QActorEventSend(ID_DONAN_ENTRANCE, "DONAN_KEEP_BEYOND")
	
end

function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)
	
	--Move Donan from Outside to Door
	Hydra.ActorSetConversationList(ID_DONAN_ENTRANCE, "")
	Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(ID_DONAN_ENTRANCE, CONVO_OPTIONAL_01)
	Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(ID_DONAN_ENTRANCE, CONVO_OPTIONAL_02)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(ID_DONAN_ENTRANCE)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(ID_DONAN_ENTRANCE, ID_LOC_DONAN_GATE, "NPC_RUN", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(ID_DONAN_ENTRANCE, ID_LOC_DONAN_GATE)
		
end

function Start()
		
	--Move Donan from Door to Magic Door
	Hydra.Wait(1)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(ID_DONAN_ENTRANCE, ID_LOC_DONAN_MAGIC, "NPC_RUN", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(ID_DONAN_ENTRANCE, ID_LOC_DONAN_MAGIC)
	
	--Donan Talks About Opening Magic Door
	Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(ID_DONAN_ENTRANCE, CONVO_DONAN_MAGIC_DOOR)
	Hydra.QActorEventSend(ID_DONAN_ENTRANCE, "DONAN_MAGIC_DOOR_DOWN")
	
end

function Start()
	
	--Donan Opens Door
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(ID_DONAN_ENTRANCE, ID_LOC_DONAN_MAGIC)
	Hydra.QActorPhasedAnimLoop(ID_DONAN_ENTRANCE, ANIM_USE, 0.46)

	--Door Opens / EventSend to Complete Phase
	Hydra.QActorEventSend(ID_DONAN_ENTRANCE, "COMPLETE")

end

function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)
	Hydra.ActorGizmoOperate(ID_MAGIC_DOOR)
	Hydra.Wait(2)
	Hydra.ActorDisable(ID_DONAN_ENTRANCE)
end
